description: Tidal ETF Trust II - Gateway Senior Secured Credit Opportunities ETF is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by Toroso Investments, LLC. Tidal ETF Trust II - Gateway Senior Secured Credit Opportunities ETF is domiciled in the United States.
